I")<p>MIDI controller based on microcontroller <strong>PIC 12F675</strong>. The source code was developed with <a href="http://www.sourceboost.com/Products/BoostC/Overview.html">BoostC compiler</a>.</p>

<p>This MIDI controller can control the following function on the stompboxes:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Scenes up and down feature</li>
  <li>Switch between folders</li>
  <li>Activate the pedal tuner</li>
  <li>Control pedal loop features</li>
</ol>

<p>Binary and source code can be found on the GitHub repository <a href="http://www.github.com/vandersonpc/m9midi">here</a> <a href="http://www.github.com/vandersonpc/m9midi"><img src="http://i.imgur.com/0o48UoR.png (github icon with padding)" alt="alt text" /></a></p>

